            Analytics cookies collect information about how you use our website, such as which pages you visit most frequently and if you experience any errors. These cookies help us improve our services and user experience.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white rounded border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
